{"tid":1744052,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"搞返場感謝美國大遊行，讓美國國旗在TG中飄蕩。","createTime":"2019-11-21T13:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T14:18:39.000Z","uid":280192,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f3985900e45d4476fb264ecff6090d2c4383ec64","tid":1744052,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:32:53.000Z","msg":"搞返場感謝美國大遊行，被驅散嘅畫面會好靚。歐美各國會見證到：係香港連感謝美國都被暴力驅散嘅荒謬。<br />\n<br />\n而且對家已經搞定星期日反美國集會，位位一千，加埋大陸西實吹到有50萬人。<br />\n<br />\n我地唔好比外國人錯覺，本港人唔想美國插手。要感謝得大力D！"},{"pid":"eb678a240aa4eb9463207fcaafbbaa93e0a188f2","tid":1744052,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T13:34:16.000Z","msg":"由六月反送中示威活動至今，警方已承認施放超過10,000發催淚彈。警方甚至喺民居或學校附近施放催淚彈，令到最近有好多小朋友有呼吸道或皮膚疾病。而且有害氣體亦會令市民，小朋友健康受到長遠影響。為咗保護下一代，我哋一班家長決定發起遊行，呼籲教育界及家長帶同小朋友一齊參加！<br />\n<br />\n遊行已獲不反對通知書， 希望各位教育界人士，家長帶埋小朋友一同進場！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊行日期：23/11(星期六)<br />\n遊行時間：10:00a.m.<br />\n遊行地點：九龍塘沙福道》喇沙小學<br />\n<br />\n活動詳情請入Tg link : <a href=\"https://t.me/StopKillingOurKids\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FStopKillingOurKids&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt8wEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=29d47727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/StopKillingOurKids</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cju0269.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCju0269.jpg&h=63e6c479&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rd7aFTR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frd7aFTR.jpg&h=ca0776ad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/twsU7yT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtwsU7yT.jpg&h=3c84c1cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dY2en7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdY2en7e.jpg&h=8a342c95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFArYFz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https